# Enforce LF for all text files in this plugin so the migration-manifest.json
# body hashes verify identically on Windows and Linux. Without this, a Windows
# clone with core.autocrlf=true would get CRLF in the working tree and the
# verifier would compare manifest LF-hashes against CRLF bodies.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.mjs text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
